WEBVTT

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:03.680
Basi, sipendi kujivunia,

00:00:03.719 --> 00:00:09.256
ila ni mzuri sana kutafuta vitu
vitakavyo niudhi.

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:11.376
Ni utaalamu wangu wa kweli.

00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:15.296
Naweza kusikia sifa 100
na tusi moja,

00:00:15.320 --> 00:00:16.816
na ni nini ninakumbuka?

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:18.216
Hilo tusi.

00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:20.936
Na kulingana na utafiti,
siko peke yangu.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:26.496
Bahati mbaya, akili ya binadamu
imeungwa kulenga mabaya.

00:00:26.520 --> 00:00:29.856
Sasa, hii inaweza kuwa imesaidia
pale tulivyokua watu wa pangoni,

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:31.736
kujaribu kuepuka wanyama pori,